  "description": "## Deep Component Audit ‚Äî hx-select\n\n**Component directory:** `packages/hx-library/src/components/hx-select/`\n**wc-mcp Health Score:** 86 (B)\n**Known issues:** 20 properties missing descriptions including formAssociated, _internals, _options, _selectedValues, _activeIndex, _searchQuery, _filteredOptions, _displayValue, and more.\n\n### wc-mcp Tools ‚Äî USE THESE\n- `score_component`, `get_component`, `analyze_accessibility`, `validate_usage`, `list_css_parts`, `list_events`, `list_slots`, `get_design_tokens`\n- **Report wc-mcp bugs to `/Volumes/Development/booked/wc-tools` board.**\n\n### Audit Scope\n1. **Design Tokens** ‚Äî `--hx-` tokens. Trigger, listbox, option highlight, scrollbar. Dark mode.\n2. **Accessibility** ‚Äî WCAG 2.1 AA. Listbox pattern. aria-expanded, aria-activedescendant. Keyboard (arrow keys, Enter, Escape, typeahead).\n3. **Functionality** ‚Äî Single/multi select. Search/filter. Placeholder. Clear. Form integration. Required. Validation. Option groups.\n4. **TypeScript** ‚Äî Strict. formAssociated. ElementInternals. No `any`.\n5. **CSS/Styling** ‚Äî Shadow DOM. CSS Parts. Listbox positioning. Responsive.\n6. **CEM Accuracy** ‚Äî Fix all 20 missing descriptions. Lowest scoring component.\n7. **Tests** ‚Äî 80%+ coverage. Selection. Multi-select. Search. Keyboard. Form. Validation.\n8. **Storybook** ‚Äî Single. Multi. Searchable. Groups. Required. Error.\n9. **Drupal Compatibility** ‚Äî Select list replacement. Twig-friendly.\n10. **Portability** ‚Äî CDN-ready. Form-associated.\n\n### Deliverable\nDetailed audit report. Fix CRITICAL+HIGH. Document rest.",
